OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FMore than 20 years after the starting
OL,7,Fwhistle first blew, the one-millionth
OL,8,Fparkrun took place on Saturday in
OL,9,FBushy park, southwest London, where
OL,10,Fthe sporting phenomenon first began,
OL,11,FITV News' Aisha Zahid reports
OL,13,FThe one millionth parkrun has taken
OL,14,Fplace with Olympic champion Dame Kelly
OL,15,FHolmes joining runners at the
OL,16,Fmilestone community event.
OL,18,FThe landmark 5k run took place at
OL,19,FBushy Park on Saturday morning, where
OL,20,Fthe very first parkrun happened more
OL,21,Fthan 20 years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
