OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781444876
OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FThere were just 13 runners and five
OL,7,Fvolunteers when Paul Sinton-Hewitt
OL,8,Forganised the first event ` then
OL,9,Fcalled Bushy Park Time Trial ` in West
OL,10,FLondon in October 2004.
OL,12,FIt has evolved into a global community
OL,13,Fof free, weekly, timed 5km parkruns on
OL,14,FSaturdays, and 2km junior parkruns on
OL,15,FSundays, with more than 2,800 event
OL,16,Flocations in 23 countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
