PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781444876
OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FRunners held cards to form a "thanks a
OL,7,Fmillion" sign at the London park on
OL,8,FSaturday, with Dame Kelly wearing a
OL,9,F"Celebrating 1m" t-shirt and comedian
OL,10,FJoe Wilkinson also taking part.
OL,12,FThe landmark event saw a large
OL,13,Fturnout, with runners queuing in
OL,14,Ffinish funnels to get their times
OL,15,Frecorded on a sunny morning in the
OL,16,Fcapital.
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@HO]qD@AOUqD@PO]
