OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FDame Kelly, who won 800m and 1500m
OL,7,Fgold medals at the 2004 Olympics,
OL,8,Fjoined parkrun founder Mr Sinton-
OL,9,FHewitt and parkrun global chief
OL,10,Fexecutive Elizabeth Duggan at the
OL,11,Fevent.
OL,13,FThe retired British middle-distance
OL,14,Fathlete said: "Parkrun has been a huge
OL,15,Fpart of my post-running career life
OL,16,Fand I know first-hand the difference
OL,17,Fit makes.
OL,26,@vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781444876
OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,F"When I line up at a parkrun, whether
OL,7,FI'm walking, running or volunteering,
OL,8,FI feel part of something really
OL,9,Fspecial.
OL,11,F"One million events is an
OL,12,Fextraordinary achievement and I'm so
OL,13,Fproud to be here at Bushy Park, where
OL,14,Fit all began, to celebrate it. Here's
OL,15,Fto the next million!"
OL,17,FComedian Joe Wilkinson, a regular
OL,18,Frunner, said the landmark was an
OL,19,F"incredible achievement".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@UO]{D@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
