OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781444876
OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FSimon Hayes, chief executive of Sport
OL,7,FEngland, said parkrun had "transformed
OL,8,Fhow millions of people approach
OL,9,Fexercise, every week, all across the
OL,10,Fcountry".
OL,12,FMr Hayes added: "Its focus on
OL,13,Faccessibility and connection has
OL,14,Fcreated a new way for people to run,
OL,15,Fwheel, walk and talk together, powered
OL,16,Fby volunteers and rooted in local
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@oD@[OUrD@HO]tD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
