OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781444876
OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,F"It delivers extraordinary benefits
OL,7,Ffor individuals, communities and the
OL,8,Fpublic purse, and we are very proud to
OL,9,Fcelebrate this historic moment with
OL,10,Fthem."
OL,12,FSpeaking before the charity reached
OL,13,Fthe milestone, Mr Sinton-Hewitt, 65,
OL,14,Fsaid a million events was "never in
OL,15,Fthe plan".
OL,17,FHe added: "Nobody ever thought we
OL,18,Fwould get to a million.
OL,20,F"But of course now the next million's
OL,21,Fgoing to come so much quicker."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@FO]vD@[OUwD@IO]yD@KOU|D@AOU}D@
OL,26,A_O]
