PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781444876
OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FMr Sinton-Hewitt said the "numbers are
OL,7,Fextraordinary", adding: "There are
OL,8,Fmany people who've been born since we
OL,9,Fstarted parkrun who just don't
OL,10,Funderstand a world where parkrun
OL,11,Fdoesn't exist."
OL,13,FHe said he does not get involved in
OL,14,Fthe day-to-day running of parkrun and
OL,15,Fis "hoping in a year or so's time to
OL,16,Fretire from the organisation".
OL,18,FIn January, the King attended
OL,19,FSandringham parkrun in Norfolk as a
OL,20,Fspectator.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@NO]oD@YOUsD@OO]wD@DOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
