PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781444876
OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FMr Sinton-Hewitt, who now lives near
OL,7,FHorsham, Sussex, said: "I'd love to
OL,8,Fmeet the King, I'd love to have them
OL,9,Finvolved on a more regular basis.
OL,11,F"But the fact he chose to go down to
OL,12,FSandringham parkrun and to cheer
OL,13,Feverybody on, that is a huge accolade
OL,14,Ffor parkrun and we're very, very proud
OL,15,Fof that."
OL,17,FHe said the success of parkrun was
OL,18,F"clearly down to the simplicity... the
OL,19,Ffact it is for everybody, inclusivity,
OL,20,Fthe nature of that, the fact that it's
OL,21,Ffree".
OL,26,@oD@XOUsD@AOUwD@IO]zD@AOU}D@EO]
