OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FThe first runner to participate in
OL,7,F1,000 parkruns, Darren Wood, reached
OL,8,Fthe milestone last month.
OL,10,FHe said he is "not running much any
OL,11,Fmore because (the) knees just can't do
OL,12,Fit" but he still tries to "do the odd
OL,13,Fwalk and quite a lot of volunteering".
OL,15,FElizabeth Duggan, chief executive
OL,16,Fofficer of parkrun Global, said
OL,17,Fhitting one million events was "just
OL,18,Fphenomenal".
OL,26,@rD@OOUtD@CO]tD@[OUuD@eO]yD@`OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
