OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781444876
OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FShe said parkrun has "massive
OL,7,Fambitions for the future", including
OL,8,Fto increase the number of parkrun
OL,9,Fcountries from 23 to 30 by 2030.
OL,11,F"We have about half a million
OL,12,Fparticipants every single weekend
OL,13,Fglobally and we believe by 2030 we
OL,14,Fwill be hitting three quarters of a
OL,15,Fmillion," Ms Duggan added.
OL,26,@nD@VOUoD@YO]sD@AOUwD@IO]
