OL,3,COne millionth parkrun takes place with
OL,4,CDame Kelly Holmes among runners
OL,6,FOver 2,200 GP surgeries are twinned
OL,7,Fwith a local parkrun as part of the
OL,8,Fparkrun practice social prescribing
OL,9,Fprogramme and more than 2,000 primary
OL,10,Fschools have signed up to parkrun
OL,11,Fprimary since its launch in September
OL,12,Flast year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
